metadata.name: Fragments of My Mind
metadata.description:
This multi-media abstract work is a vibrantly colorful and deeply layered representation of the artists mind and the constant barrage of thoughts, ideas, dreams, fears and insecurities that consume it on a daily basis.  
Made with acrylic paints, charcoals, pastels, plaster, ink and spray paint the work embodies the versatility of the artist, his tools and mediums.


Completed in 2021  
Showcased in 2021 with Conception Global Art Collective
